    <item>
      <title>黛安·阿博特在调查后恢复工党党鞭职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/diane-abbott-has-labour-party-whip-restored-after-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[资深议员黛安·阿博特 (Diane Abbott) 因种族主义争议而被停职，现已恢复工党党鞭职务，但目前尚不清楚她是否会被允许在即将举行的大选中代表该党参选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/diane-abbott-has-labour-party-whip-restored-after-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 20:56:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党将通过网络提名拜登，以便他能够进入俄亥俄州的选票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/biden-will-get-dnc-virtual-nomination-to-appear-on-ohio-ballot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党全国委员会计划在大会召开前通过网络唱名提名方式提名总统乔·拜登，以确保他在俄亥俄州获得选票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/biden-will-get-dnc-virtual-nomination-to-appear-on-ohio-ballot</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 20:54:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫称以色列袭击拉法赫没有越过红线</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/white-house-says-israel-s-rafah-strike-doesn-t-cross-red-line</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫表示，以色列对拉法赫营地的袭击造成数十人死亡，这是毁灭性的，但这不会导致总统乔·拜登冻结向该国运送更多武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/white-house-says-israel-s-rafah-strike-doesn-t-cross-red-line</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 20:49:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普陪审团被敦促拒绝有关合法记录的“谎言”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/trump-was-victim-of-extortion-lawyer-tells-hush-money-jurors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在其封口费刑事审判中的律师告诉陪审员，该案的核心商业记录与支付给他的前律师和调解人迈克尔·科恩的合法款项有关，他说陪审员应该拒绝接受科恩的证词。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/trump-was-victim-of-extortion-lawyer-tells-hush-money-jurors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 18:06:21 GMT</pubDate>
